"Add oil and sauté <b>4 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add tomato purée, water, pepper and stock cube, cook <b>4 min\/120°C\/speed 1<b> then blend <b>20 sec\/speed 8<b>."},{"content":"Spread tomato and chorizo ​​sauce over potato base. Cover with spinach and slices of tomato, season with nutmeg (if using), sprinkle with Gouda and bake for 20 minutes (200°C), covering with baking paper if necessary after 10 minutes."},{"content":"Cut pizza in 12 slices and serve hot or cold."}],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","1h 5m","12 slices"]}